Usage: deletePtnCut [-help] { -ptn {ptnName | ptnNameList} | -all  }

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
-all                                   # Specifies all partitions
                                       # (bool, optional)
-ptn {ptnName | ptnNameList}           # Specifies name(s) of the partition(s).
                                       # (string, optional)